query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `cart_events` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `userId` int,
  `sessionId` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `eventType` enum('cart_viewed','item_added','item_removed','checkout_started','checkout_abandoned','checkout_completed') NOT NULL,
  `productId` int,
  `variantId` int,
  `quantity` int,
  `cartSnapshot` json,
  `userAgent` text,
  `ipAddress` varchar(45),
  `referrer` text,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `cart_events_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  KEY `user_id_idx` (`userId`),
  KEY `session_id_idx` (`sessionId`),
  KEY `event_type_idx` (`eventType`),
  KEY `created_at_idx` (`createdAt`)
);
